"use strict";(self.webpackChunkwangdoc=self.webpackChunkwangdoc||[]).push([[136],{87004:(e,a,n)=>{n.r(a),n.d(a,{data:()=>s});const s={key:"v-4364a25a",path:"/git-tutorial/branch.html",title:"分支",lang:"zh-CN",frontmatter:{summary:"分支 分支是 Git 最重要的概念之一，也是最常用的操作之一。几乎所有 Git 操作流程都离不开分支。 git branch命令可以列出本地的所有分支。 创建一个名为MyBranch的新分支，但是依然停留在当前分支。 在远程主机origin上创建一个MyBranch的分支，并与本地的同名分支建立追踪关系。 将当前分支改名为MyBranch。 删除MyBran",head:[["meta",{property:"og:url",content:"https://yzqbooks.github.io/wangdoc/wangdoc/git-tutorial/branch.html"}],["meta",{property:"og:site_name",content:"wangdoc"}],["meta",{property:"og:title",content:"分支"}],["meta",{property:"og:type",content:"article"}],["meta",{property:"og:updated_time",content:"2022-04-06T10:09:00.000Z"}],["meta",{property:"og:locale",content:"zh-CN"}],["meta",{property:"article:modified_time",content:"2022-04-06T10:09:00.000Z"}]]},excerpt:"",headers:[],git:{createdTime:164923974e4,updatedTime:164923974e4,contributors:[{name:"yzqdev",email:"yzqdev@outlook.com",commits:1}]},readingTime:{minutes:.79,words:238},filePathRelative:"git-tutorial/branch.md"}},82414:(e,a,n)=>{n.r(a),n.d(a,{default:()=>r});const s=(0,n(66252).uE)('<h1 id="分支" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#分支" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 分支</h1><p>分支是 Git 最重要的概念之一，也是最常用的操作之一。几乎所有 Git 操作流程都离不开分支。</p><p><code>git branch</code>命令可以列出本地的所有分支。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> branch\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>创建一个名为<code>MyBranch</code>的新分支，但是依然停留在当前分支。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> branch MyBranch\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>在远程主机<code>origin</code>上创建一个<code>MyBranch</code>的分支，并与本地的同名分支建立追踪关系。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> push -u origin MyBranch\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>将当前分支改名为<code>MyBranch</code>。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> branch -m MyBranch\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>删除<code>MyBranch</code>分支，前提是该分支没有未合并的变动。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> branch -d MyBranch\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>强制删除<code>MyBranch</code>分支，不管有没有未合并变化。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> branch -D MyBranch\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>切换到<code>MyBranch</code>分支，当前的工作区会变为<code>MyBranch</code>分支的内容。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> checkout MyBranch\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>基于<code>MyBranch</code>分支创建一个新的<code>NewBranch</code>分支，新的<code>NewBranch</code>分支将成为当前的工作区。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>$ <span class="token function">git</span> checkout -b NewBranch MyBranch\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div>',18),c={},r=(0,n(83744).Z)(c,[["render",function(e,a){return s}]])},83744:(e,a)=>{a.Z=(e,a)=>{const n=e.__vccOpts||e;for(const[e,s]of a)n[e]=s;return n}}}]);